    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■关于本体验版</h2>本作品为《真·女神转生Ⅴ Vengeance》的免费体验版，<br>可供您游玩游戏开篇第一个区域的全部内容。<br>此外，在本体验版中创建的保存数据可在正式版中继续使用。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/0460ccbfe0a806ebfa7cba73ed92cf1a.poster.avif?t=1763531804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/0460ccbfe0a806ebfa7cba73ed92cf1a.webm?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/0460ccbfe0a806ebfa7cba73ed92cf1a.mp4?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在本体验版中，您可在游戏开篇的广阔区域中探索，体验本作的众多要素。<br>・在《真·女神转生Ⅴ》的“创世女神篇”和《真·女神转生Ⅴ Vengeance》中新增的“复仇女神篇”这两个故事中做出选择<br>・在荒废后恶魔肆虐的另一个东京——被称为“达识”的广阔世界中探索<br>・挑战多达4名剧情头目和大约20个支线任务<br>・捣毁6个恶魔巢穴，解放自己的神之力量<br>・将众多恶魔收入麾下并通过合体创造出新的恶魔，打造极致队伍<br><br>※完成本体验版的主线内容后，可在第一个区域<br>自由提升等级或完成支线任务。<br>※请注意，若在游玩正式版后游玩体验版，正式版的保存数据将被覆盖。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/457c5e0ba86815612b0083977821b963.poster.avif?t=1763531804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/457c5e0ba86815612b0083977821b963.webm?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/457c5e0ba86815612b0083977821b963.mp4?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■关于《真·女神转生Ⅴ Vengeance》<br>“真·女神转生”系列拥有宏大的世界观，其中会出现世界各地神话中的神明和恶魔，游戏系统也极具深度，是一个广受欢迎的RPG系列。<br>《真·女神转生Ⅴ Vengeance》为本系列于2024年6月14日发售的作品。<br><br>主角误闯谜之世界“达识”，在那里与一位神秘男子融合，<br>成为了触犯禁忌的“创毘”。他将投身于一场神与魔之间的战争。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/7eea8c0b46ecaa11df740865678cce70.poster.avif?t=1763531804\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/7eea8c0b46ecaa11df740865678cce70.webm?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>游戏系统最大的特色莫过于可将敌对恶魔收为同伴一同战斗的“仲魔”系统，<br>以及让恶魔合体从而创造出新恶魔的“恶魔合体”系统。<br>从个性迥异的众多恶魔中挑选队伍成员，组成只属于你的最强队伍，<br>向强大的神魔们发起挑战吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/4ca2884adaaeb41e4216fde9d3d79187.poster.avif?t=1763531804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/4ca2884adaaeb41e4216fde9d3d79187.webm?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/4ca2884adaaeb41e4216fde9d3d79187.mp4?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本作拥有在开发系列作品的过程中不断得到进化的游戏系统，<br>以及在易玩性上精益求精的游戏界面。<br>无论是RPG新手还是高手，都能充分享受游戏内容。<br><br>此前从未接触过本系列的玩家，也请一定借此机会尝试本作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/9bf61f1eedd0026e906d8a2678f3b68d.poster.avif?t=1763531804\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/9bf61f1eedd0026e906d8a2678f3b68d.webm?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185590/extras/9bf61f1eedd0026e906d8a2678f3b68d.mp4?t=1763531804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
